Add Brainrot City hub + central arena coin-task event

New shared world hub players travel to from their plot:

- HubService (server): builds a shared city plaza with a parody skyline (Brainrot
  Tower, Ohio Plaza, Sus Bank HQ, Rizz Mall, Goblinpay), shop/trade kiosks, a Kart
  Garage, and a central "Brainrot Arena". Runs the arena event loop: glowing coin
  orbs spawn periodically (500–2500 each) that anyone can grab; pushes profile so
  the HUD updates instantly. Wires teleport pads both ways.
- PlotService: each plot gets a neon "Brainrot City" pad (step on to travel) and
  exposes getSpawnCFrame so the hub can send players home.
- KartService: KartSpawner pads may now be ownerless (shared Kart Garage).
- HubController (client): clicking a kiosk opens its panel (Shop/Trade) locally.

Reaches the hub via ToCityPad → hubSpawnCFrame; returns via ToStadiumPad pads.

